### Helm Unit Testing

The boilerplate includes comprehensive Helm unit testing using the `helm-unittest` plugin:

- **Test Coverage**: All chart resources and features
- **Test Suites**: Deployment, Service, Ingress, ConfigMap, Secret, HPA, ServiceAccount
- **Test Assertions**: Resource validation, value checking, edge cases
- **Test Reports**: Coverage reports, HTML reports, JUnit XML reports
- **Test Development**: Watch mode, debug mode, performance testing

#### Test Structure

```
deploy/charts/{{ project_slug }}/tests/
├── deployment_test.yaml      # Deployment resource tests
├── service_test.yaml         # Service resource tests
├── ingress_test.yaml         # Ingress resource tests
├── configmap_test.yaml       # ConfigMap resource tests
├── secret_test.yaml          # Secret resource tests
├── hpa_test.yaml             # HPA resource tests
├── serviceaccount_test.yaml  # ServiceAccount resource tests
└── _helpers_test.yaml        # Template helper tests
```

